packets.name: Flip Flop "precious pink", left
packets.author: Pixls
packets.description: The precious pink sibling of Lorex Voxilette is the perfect summer companion: lightweight and super endurable, they are also sustainable because they are made of recycled voxels! This is the left shoe. Relax in style this summer with Lorex for PIXL (pixls.eth | ethical blockchain fashion from Austria). Manufactured with MagicaVoxel.
